{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 38,
    "name": "سُورَةُ صٓ",
    "englishName": "Saad",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The letter Saad",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 88,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 3971,
        "text": "薩德。指著名的《古蘭經》發誓。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3972,
        "text": "不然！不信道者，是妄自尊大、違背真理的。",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3973,
        "text": "在他們之前我曾毀滅了許多世代，他們呼號，但逃亡的時機已逝去了。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3974,
        "text": "他們驚訝，因為他們本族中的警告者來臨他們。不信道的人們說：「這是一個術士，是一個說謊者。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3975,
        "text": "難道他要將許多神靈變成一個神靈嗎？這確是一件怪事。」",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3976,
        "text": "他們中的貴族們起身說：「你們走罷！你們堅忍著崇拜你們的眾神靈罷！這確是一件前定的事。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3977,
        "text": "在最後的宗教中，我們沒有聽見這種話，這種話只是偽造的。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3978,
        "text": "難道教誨降於他，而不降於我們嗎？」不然！他們對於我的教訓，是在懷疑之中，不然！他們還沒有嘗試我的刑罰。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3979,
        "text": "難道他們有你萬能的、博施的主的慈恩的庫藏嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3980,
        "text": "難道他們有天地萬物的國權嗎？假若他們有，就叫他們緣天梯而上升吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3981,
        "text": "他們是由各黨派聯合起來的烏合之眾，他們將要在那裡敗北。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3982,
        "text": "在他們之前，曾否認使者的，有努哈的宗族、阿德人、有武力的法老、",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3983,
        "text": "賽莫德人、魯特的宗族、茂林的居民。這些都是黨派，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3984,
        "text": "他們之中沒有一個未曾否認使者的，所以我的懲罰是必然的。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 391,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3985,
        "text": "這些人，只等待一聲喊叫，那是不耽擱一霎時的。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3986,
        "text": "他們說：「我們的主啊！在清算日之前，請你快將我們所應得的刑罰，降於我們吧！」",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 453,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3987,
        "text": "你當忍受他們所說的話，你當記憶我的僕人——有能力的達五德，他確是歸依真主的。",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 454,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3988,
        "text": "我確已使諸山服從他，他們早晚讚頌。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 454,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3989,
        "text": "並使眾鳥集合起來，統統都服從他。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 454,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3990,
        "text": "我鞏固他的國權，我賞賜他智慧和文辭。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 454,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3991,
        "text": "兩造來告狀的故事來臨你了嗎？當時，他們逾牆而入內殿。",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 454,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3992,
        "text": "當時，他們去見達五德，他為他們而恐怖。他們說：「你不要恐怖！我們是兩造，被告曾欺凌了原告，請你為我們秉公裁判，請你不要偏袒，請你指引我們正路。",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 454,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3993,
        "text": "這個確是我的朋友，他有九十九隻母綿羊，我有一隻母綿羊，他卻說，『你把牠讓給我吧！』他在辯論方面戰勝我。」",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 454,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3994,
        "text": "達五德說：「他確已欺負你了，因為他要求你把你的母綿羊歸併他的母綿羊。有許多伙計，的確相欺，惟信道而行善者則不然，但他們是很少的。」達五德以為我考驗他，他就向他的主求饒，且拜倒下去，並歸依他。※",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 454,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": {
          "id": 11,
          "recommended": true,
          "obligatory": false
        }
      },
      {
        "number": 3995,
        "text": "我就饒了他的過失，他在我那裡，的確獲得寵愛和優美的歸宿。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 454,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3996,
        "text": "達五德啊！我確已任命你為大地的代治者，你當替人民秉公判決，不要順從私欲，以免私欲使你叛離真主的大道；叛離真主的大道者，將因忘卻清算之日而受嚴厲的刑罰。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 454,
        "ruku": 392,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3997,
        "text": "我沒有徒然地創造天地萬物，那是不信道者的猜測。悲哉！不信道的人們將受火刑。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3998,
        "text": "難道我使信道而且行善者，像在地方作惡者一樣嗎？難道我使敬畏者，像放肆的人一樣嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3999,
        "text": "這是我所降示你的一本吉祥的經典，以便他們沉思經中的節文，以便有理智的人們覺悟。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4000,
        "text": "我將素萊曼賜予達五德，那個僕人真是優美！他確是歸依真主的。",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4001,
        "text": "當時，他在傍晚，檢閱能靜立、能奔馳的馬隊。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4002,
        "text": "他說：「我的確為記憶我的主而喜好馬隊，直到牠們被帷幕遮住了。」",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4003,
        "text": "他說：「你們將牠們趕回來罷！」他就著手撫摩那些馬的腿部和頸部。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4004,
        "text": "我確已考驗素萊曼，我曾將一個肉體投在他的寶座上，然後，他歸依真主。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4005,
        "text": "他說：「我的主啊！求你赦宥我，求你賞賜我一個非任何人所宜繼承的國權。你確是博施的。」",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4006,
        "text": "我曾為他制服了風，風奉著他的命令習習流向他所欲到的地方。",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4007,
        "text": "我又為他制服了一切能建築的或能潛水的惡魔，",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4008,
        "text": "以及其他許多帶腳鐐的惡魔。",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4009,
        "text": "「這是我所特賜你的，你可以將它施給別人，也可以將它保留起來，你總是不受清算的。」",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4010,
        "text": "他在我那裡，的確獲得寵愛和優美的歸宿。",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 393,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4011,
        "text": "你應當記憶我的僕人安優卜。當時，他祈禱他的主說：「惡魔確已使我遭受辛苦和刑罰。」",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4012,
        "text": "「你用腳踏地吧！這是可用以沐浴和可用作飲料的涼水。」",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 455,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4013,
        "text": "我曾以他的眷屬，和像他們的，同齊賞賜他。那是由我降下的慈恩，也是由於教誨有理智的人們。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4014,
        "text": "「你當親手拿一把草，用它去打擊一下。你不要違背誓約。」我確已發現他是堅忍的，那僕人真優美！他確是歸依真主的，",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4015,
        "text": "你應當記憶我的僕人易卜拉欣、易司哈格、葉爾孤白，他們都是有能力、有眼光的。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4016,
        "text": "我使他們成為真誠的人，因為他們有一種純潔的德性——常念後世。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4017,
        "text": "他們在我那裡，確是特選的，確是純善的。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4018,
        "text": "你當記憶易司馬儀、艾勒葉賽爾、助勒基福勒，他們都是純善的。",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4019,
        "text": "這是一種教誨。敬畏的人們，必得享受優美的歸宿——",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4020,
        "text": "永久的樂園，園門是為他們常開的。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4021,
        "text": "他們在園中，靠在床上；他們在園中叫人拿種種水果和飲料來。",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 182,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4022,
        "text": "他們有不視非禮的、同年的伴侶。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4023,
        "text": "這是應許你們在清算日之後得享受的。",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4024,
        "text": "這確是我的給養，它將永不罄盡。",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4025,
        "text": "這是事實。放蕩者必定要得一個最惡的歸宿——",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4026,
        "text": "那就是火獄，他們將入其中。那臥褥真惡劣！",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4027,
        "text": "這是事實。他們將嘗試刑罰，那刑罰是很熱的飲料，和很冷的飲料，",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4028,
        "text": "還有別的同樣惡劣的各種飲料。",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4029,
        "text": "這些是與你們一齊突進的隊伍，他們不受歡迎，他們必入火獄。",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4030,
        "text": "他們將說：「不然！你們才是不受歡迎的，你們曾把我們誘惑到這種境地，這歸宿真惡劣！」",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4031,
        "text": "他們將說：「我們的主啊！誰把我們誘惑到這種境地，求你使誰在火獄中受加倍的刑罰。」",
        "numberInSurah": 61,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 456,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4032,
        "text": "他們將說：「有許多人，從前我們認為他們是惡人，現在怎麼不見他們呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 62,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4033,
        "text": "我們曾把他們當笑柄呢？還是我們過去看不起他們呢？」",
        "numberInSurah": 63,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4034,
        "text": "居火獄者的爭論是必然的。",
        "numberInSurah": 64,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 394,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4035,
        "text": "你說：「我只是一個警告者。除獨一至尊的真主外，絕無應受崇拜的。",
        "numberInSurah": 65,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4036,
        "text": "他是天地萬物的主，他是萬能的、至赦的。」",
        "numberInSurah": 66,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4037,
        "text": "你說：「那是一個重大的消息，",
        "numberInSurah": 67,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4038,
        "text": "你們卻離棄它。",
        "numberInSurah": 68,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4039,
        "text": "當上界的眾天神爭論的時候，我不知道他們的情形。",
        "numberInSurah": 69,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4040,
        "text": "我只奉到啟示說我是一個坦率的警告者。」",
        "numberInSurah": 70,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4041,
        "text": "當時，你的主曾對眾天神說：「我必定要用泥創造一個人，",
        "numberInSurah": 71,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4042,
        "text": "當我把他造出來，並將我的精神吹入他的體內的時候，你們當為他而倒身叩頭。」",
        "numberInSurah": 72,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4043,
        "text": "眾天神全體一同叩頭，",
        "numberInSurah": 73,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4044,
        "text": "惟易卜劣廝自大，他原是不信道者。",
        "numberInSurah": 74,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4045,
        "text": "主說：「易卜劣廝啊！你怎麼不肯對我親手造的人叩頭呢？你自大呢？還是你本是高尚的呢？」",
        "numberInSurah": 75,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4046,
        "text": "他說：「我比他高貴；你用火造我，用泥造他。」",
        "numberInSurah": 76,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4047,
        "text": "主說：「你從樂園中出去吧！你確是被放逐的，",
        "numberInSurah": 77,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4048,
        "text": "你必遭我的棄絕，直到報應日。」",
        "numberInSurah": 78,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4049,
        "text": "他說：「我的主啊！求你寬待我到人類復活之日。」",
        "numberInSurah": 79,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4050,
        "text": "主說：「你必定被寬待，",
        "numberInSurah": 80,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4051,
        "text": "直到復活時來臨之日。」",
        "numberInSurah": 81,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4052,
        "text": "他說：「以你的尊榮發誓，我必將他們全體加以誘惑，",
        "numberInSurah": 82,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4053,
        "text": "惟不誘惑你的純潔的僕人。」",
        "numberInSurah": 83,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 457,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4054,
        "text": "他說：「我的話確是真理，我只說真理；",
        "numberInSurah": 84,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 458,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4055,
        "text": "我必以你和人類中順從你的，同齊充滿火獄。」",
        "numberInSurah": 85,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 458,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4056,
        "text": "你說：「我不為傳達使命而向你們索取任何報酬，我不是冒名的。（或弄虛作假的）。",
        "numberInSurah": 86,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 458,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4057,
        "text": "這只是對全世界的教誨，",
        "numberInSurah": 87,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 458,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4058,
        "text": "在一個時期之後，你們必定知道關於這教誨的消息。」",
        "numberInSurah": 88,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 458,
        "ruku": 395,
        "hizbQuarter": 183,
        "sajda": false
      }
